summary: Makes your alchemy skill affect your potions more. Your choice of 2x, 3x, 4x, or 5x stronger.
descriptionHtml:
Makes your alchemy skill affect your potions more. Your choice of 2x, 3x, 4x, or 5x stronger.

I created this mod in an attempt to make alchemy level faster. This was the result. I now have my original intention working and available for download here: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1108

Check out my other mods from my profile here:
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/modules/members/index.php?id=3056619
author: tmonet
